    "summary": "The user engages in highly stylized, poetic expressions of suicidal ideation, framing death as a \"graceful\" or \"poetic\" exit to preserve their current sorrow. The assistant responds to every prompt with the exact same repetitive canned response, which acknowledges the pain but explicitly rejects the notion of self-harm and encourages living.",
